# VITE_API_URL intentionally omitted — production uses the /api Vercel proxy
# so session cookies are sent same-origin. Direct Render URL bypasses the proxy
# and causes 401s due to cross-origin cookie blocking.

# Analytics (PostHog). Set these in the Vercel project env vars, not here, so
# the key is managed outside the repo. The project API key is a public client
# key and is safe to expose in the browser bundle.
#   VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#   VITE_POSTHOG_HOST=https://us.i.posthog.com   # use https://eu.i.posthog.com for EU
